# Change keybindings for moving between workspaces. There will be a problem with 4-buttons
# shortcuts, so install dconf-editor package.
sudo apt-get install dconf-editor
Run it and go through the path:
org.gnome.desktop.wm.keybindings
There are all the shortcuts that can be manually modified

Maybe there is some CLI way. There is a dconf-cli package. Have not tryed it yet.


